
- Graphics
  - Drawing game objects
    - Asteroids
    - Ship
    - Bullets
    - Particles
  - HUD
    - Score
    - Lives
- Gameplay
  - User input
    - Ship control
      - Up, Down, Accelerate, Decelerate
    - Game control
      - Escape, Window closed
  - Clock tick
    - Update game
      - Move asteroids
      - Move bullets
      - Move player
      - Check collisions
        - Delete and create asteroids and bullets as needed
      - Move particles
    - Draw game
    - Flip surface
    - Check game is still running

- BUGS
